[1m[34;41m∫[1m[37;41mThese never work as they come and will have to be extensively modified by    [1m[34;41m∫[40m
[1m[34;41m∫[1m[37;41myou. And since they generally only run at 3 AM, you will have to be awake    [1m[34;41m∫[40m
[1m[34;41m∫[1m[37;41mto see just how they die and then try to fix it.                             [1m[34;41m∫[40m
[1m[34;41m∫[1m[37;41m                                                                             [1m[34;41m∫[40m
